\begin_inset Formula $N\vartriangleleft G$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

 is a subgroup of 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

 is a subgroup of 
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

